+/**
+ * filemap_get_folios_tag - Get a batch of folios matching @tag
+ * @mapping:    The address_space to search
+ * @start:      The starting page index
+ * @end:        The final page index (inclusive)
+ * @tag:        The tag index
+ * @fbatch:     The batch to fill
